data.description: Custom luxury home. 4 bed 2.75 bath on 1.89 acres. Grand entry w/ curved staircase, floor to ceiling windows, office, sauna, hardwoods, custom tiling & crown-molding throughout! Large kitchen next to family room w/ granite counters, stainless steel appliances & plenty of storage space. Two decks to enjoy for year-round entertainment. Master has gorgeous 5-pce bath with a double closet. Close to major highways & plenty of shopping! Lot could potentially be subdivided. Zoning R4, Four DU per acre.    Seller to remove personal building supply's and material for up to 90 days after closing from the yard rent free.
